This project aims at creating a simple usenet like server in C++.


BUILD
=====

Running make all will result in three binaries in the bin/ dir.
Some things from c++11 is required, most notably the auto keyword and
lambdas. GCC 4.5+ should be able to build it just fine.


Usage
=====

Usage: ./client HOST PORT

Usage: ./serverdisk PORT PATH
Start server on port PORT with database on PATH

Usage: ./servermem PORT
Start server on port PORT


Database
========

The database structure:
.
├── 1
│   ├── 1
│   │   ├── author
│   │   ├── body
│   │   └── title
│   ├── 2
│   │   ├── author
│   │   ├── body
│   │   └── title
│   └── name
└── 2
    ├── 1
    │   ├── author
    │   ├── body
    │   └── title
    ├── 2
    │   ├── author
    │   ├── body
    │   └── title
    └── name

